## 问题检测详情

### 问题 1: tasks.md 不同步

```bash
CLI_PROGRESS=$(echo "$APPLY_RESULT" | jq '.progress.complete')
ACTUAL=$(grep -c "\- \[x\]" openspec/changes/"$CHANGE_NAME"/tasks.md)

echo "⚠️ 状态不同步"
echo "  CLI 报告: $CLI_PROGRESS"
echo "  实际 tasks.md: $ACTUAL"
echo ""
echo "建议：重新检查 tasks.md 或执行 /opsx-plan 刷新"
```

### 问题 2: worktree 有未提交更改

```bash
echo "⚠️ Worktree 有未提交的更改"
git status --short
echo ""
echo "建议：先 commit 再继续"
echo "  git add -A && git commit -m 'WIP: $CHANGE_NAME'"
```

### 问题 3: 计划文件过期

```bash
PLAN_TIME=$(stat -c %Y .sisyphus/plans/"$CHANGE_NAME".md 2>/dev/null || echo "0")
TASKS_TIME=$(stat -c %Y openspec/changes/"$CHANGE_NAME"/tasks.md 2>/dev/null || echo "0")

if [ "$TASKS_TIME" -gt "$PLAN_TIME" ]; then
    echo "⚠️ tasks.md 比计划文件新"
    echo "建议：/opsx-plan $CHANGE_NAME 重新生成计划"
fi
```

